katsuyōgo (活用語), word classes which have inflections

  dōshi (動詞), verbs,
  keiyōshi (形容詞), i-type adjectives.
  keiyōdōshi (形容動詞), na-type adjectives (literally "adjectival verb")



hikatsuyōgo (非活用語) or 無活用語 (mukatsuyōgo), word classes which do not have inflections

  meishi (名詞), nouns
  daimeishi (代名詞), pronouns
  fukushi (副詞), adverbs
  setsuzokushi (接続詞), conjunctions
  kandōshi (感動詞), interjections
  rentaishi (連体詞), prenominals

